{"tid":1949530,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"港台回應世衛訪問爭議：記者平實提出問題","createTime":"2020-03-29T16:54:31.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-30T01:16:44.000Z","uid":36073,"like":63,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"2a661acce2d679fb06f183806da1de4d879401e3","tid":1949530,"uid":36073,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-29T16:54:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.lih.kg/540/https://na.cx/i/2Qm9d02.gif\" /><br />\n<br />\n香港電台機構傳訊及節目標準總監伍曼儀回應《蘋果》查詢：「大家看片段也看到，她是作為記者很平實地去問，當時線路（網絡）有問題切了斷，之後重新接駁再問，他（艾沃德）亦有再回答，世衞組織此後也出了聲明說明同一件事（台灣問題），整件事就是這麼簡單。」伍曼儀補充：「其實當時我們都沒有甚麼特別（意思），只是台灣這事情都是大家關心，其實我們的記者都是平實地提問，沒有甚麼特別。」<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20200329/KFTFJBVVD7IEHOLEWSYI7YI3TY/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20200329%2FKFTFJBVVD7IEHOLEWSYI7YI3TY%2F&d=UCtUugLpQcFJMmY1nWpYq5bpPLVkgxcsq72qYZiHPFQ%3D&h=1929c401\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20200329%2FKFTFJBVVD7IEHOLEWSYI7YI3TY%2F&h=1559c869\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20200329/KFTFJBVVD7IEHOLEWSYI7YI3TY/</a><br />\n<br />\nBtw 記者 IG 同 Twitter 仍然受五毛大量侮辱言語攻擊，因為黨媒已經將條訪問擺上熱門瘋傳，各位要繼續留言支持呀！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n請多多往記者嘅其他 post留言<br />\nIG<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/yvonnetg_/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fyvonnetg_%2F&d=UCtUugLpQcFJMmY1nWpYq5bpPLVkgxcsq72qYZiHPFQ%3D&h=f57d201b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/yvonnetg_/</a><br />\nTwitter<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/yvonne_tg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fyvonne_tg&d=UCtUugLpQcFJMmY1nWpYq5bpPLVkgxcsq72qYZiHPFQ%3D&h=c381b1ae\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/yvonne_tg</a><br />\nYouTube 該集訪問<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=RLvg0KnTKhU&amp;t=1146s\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DRLvg0KnTKhU%26t%3D1146s&d=UCtUugLpQcFJMmY1nWpYq5bpPLVkgxcsq72qYZiHPFQ%3D&h=af8907e6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=RLvg0KnTKhU&amp;t=1146s</a>"},{"pid":"426551cf022b2bbe3c42a2a7ed5a61e1511b7a7c","tid":1949530,"uid":54824,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-29T16:58:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/chXHH2e.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FchXHH2e.png&h=cf32ca80&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"942b28c1ade488248efadc3fe6c3b139b680636a","tid":1949530,"uid":307203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-29T16:58:37.000Z","msg":"[更新版]到底大家撐唔撐港台<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1949128\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1949128</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"d0f274be2bd52571b7f2566f41a0c54b76c02bc5","tid":1949530,"uid":40267,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-29T16:59:21.000Z","msg":"認真 港台命不久矣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好好珍惜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e72c80416b65373c73dc294ed39f0b047f7487a0","tid":1949530,"uid":36073,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"426551cf022b2bbe3c42a2a7ed5a61e1511b7a7c","tid":1949530,"uid":54824,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-29T16:58:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/chXHH2e.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2F